  <acronym>PRIMOVAR-1</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomized Phase II Clinical Trial to Select Primary Chemotherapy With Carboplatin and Docetaxel in Patients With Advanced Ovarian Cancer Stage FIGO IIIC and IV</official_title>
