  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate response to neoadjuvant chemotherapy by imaging and
      observation of anatomical and biological indicators (i.e. ascites or continuous measurement
      of tumor marker CA 125). Furthermore the optimal number of preoperative administered cycles
      of combination chemotherapy with carboplatin and docetaxel should be determined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
